Introducing Elevon X – a futuristic lifestyle shoe with elevated materials and advanced tech.⚡️

Elevon X creative was brought to life with the help of @pleid.st, an independent creative CGI design studio based in Madrid, Spain. Like HOKA, Pleid St. shares a love of innovation, always striving to experiment with their computer-generated imagery while staying inspired by nature, culture, art, music, technology, and their intersections. 

Step into the future with the new Elevon X, linked in bio.
